- Issue: https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/issues/9039
- PR (original breaking change): https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/pull/62816
- PR (additional opt-outs & metadata): https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/pull/63283

